This paper is likely to belong to the Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC) sub-category as it deals with managing support tickets and customer relationships, which are important aspects of user experience. The paper also involves data mining and predictive modelling, which could fall under Information Retrieval (cs.IR) and Database (cs.DB) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper discusses the challenges of managing support tickets in large, multi-product organizations, which could be relevant to Software Engineering (cs.SE) and Cybersecurity (cs.CY) sub-categories.
